{
  "stem": "25423.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't wish to continue, either government career or military career or a political career.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go back to academia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You went into--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Economics, to make a living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started as a messenger boy on Wall Street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I, as you can see, have no [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sensitivity on the subject, and therefore I communicated with a variety of people on what has happened.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And survivors, other survivors visited me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my children are fully aware of my background.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Besides, I became involved in the process of beatification of this Archbishop Metropolitan.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was called to testify as a witness, because I'm one of the few people who lived with him and worked in his archives.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was called to testify in the process of beatification in Rome.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What it involved is that my testimony was concentrated on two things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, on the behavior of this Archbishop Metropolitan during the Holocaust, the fact that he came out with an open, pastoral letter condemning the killing of Jews and warning his flock not to participate, directly or indirectly, in this horror.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the pastoral letter's title is, 'You Shall Not Kill.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is one point.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Secondly, he also organized, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the monastic orders in his diocese, formal action of saving Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to my amazement, with time, it became apparent to me that there were more than 200 people saved.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's recorded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's a file on the subject in the Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Clement was recognized as Righteous by Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So was Steck-- Father Steck and the Studites.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They have some questions about the Metropolitan because of controversies which were injected by Poles, by KGB, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
